metadata.title: MACKLEMORE & RYAN LEWIS - CAN'T HOLD US FEAT. RAY DALTON
metadata.creator: Macklemore

tracks.text: An elderly black man stares at us. He has a white beard and dreadlocks.
Across a snowy hill, rapper Macklemore walks towards the man. Macklemore wears a wolfskin on his head.
The black man pulls a black and white trifolded flag out of the snow.
Macklemore ties the flag to a stick. It's has 13 black and white stripes. In the top left of the flag reads "The Heist".
Macklemore runs through the woods, then climbs on a dog sled.
The dogs run.
He runs through the snowy woods
He runs through dry woods.
He runs up to a sea plane.
The flag flies out of the sea plane.
It falls in woods.
A muscular, shirtless black man leads a camel over a sand dune towards woods.
Macklemore raps to us on a ship. Several sails fly from the ship's 50ft mast. Dozens of people dance around him.
Macklemore raps on a peach wearing a marching band jacket
The muscular black man finds the flag in the woods.
A kangaroo hops along the dunes near the camel
The man carries the flag to the camel
He carries the flag while riding the camel across dunes, and down an alley. Macklemore takes the camel's lead.
Macklemore leads the camel and flag into a large crowd of people. He stands on a stage and they reach towards him.
DJ Ryan Lewis looks down at the crowd through a second floor window.
He jumps from the window. People watch from nearby rooftops. The crowd catches him.
R&B singer Ray Dalton sings on a street with palm trees in the background.
Lewis crowdsurfs to the camel and takes the flag.
Lewis rides the motorcycle across rolling green hills. The flag flies behind him.
A red truck drives across a field, towing a flat trailer. The trailer hosts a living room setup with a couch, lamp, and TV. Macklemore gets up from the couch.
Macklemore raps from the beach. Lewis rides through a misty sunset.
On the ship, Lewis emerges from below deck, carrying the flag.
He climbs up the front of the boat, and walks up the bowsprit, dangling over the ocean.
Lewis dives into the ocean.
On a white beach, Dalton sits in a barbers chair. Macklemore brushes and trims his curly hair.
Lewis emerges from the ocean behind them.
Lewis puts the flag down. Dalton, now with a close shaved head, stands and takes the flag.
Dalton carries the flag down the beach. On a rooftop, the muscular man plays a horn with 20 other brass players.
Dalton rows a boat through a jungle.
DDalton walks in a creek.
Macklemore shouts down to a crowd at night
Ship. Camel. Dogs. Seaplane. Wolfskin. Snow.
Dalton ties the flag to a rocket on a beach.
In the moonlight, Dalton lights the rocket.
Red light shoots into the sky.
A sky diver falls, leaving a trail of red smoke.
The sky diver lands on top of the Seattle space needle. It's Macklemore, and he has the flag.
He raises the flag.
The flag flies. The suburbs and water are in the distance.
Downtown Seattle is behind the flag.
Macklemore falls back onto the couch on the trailer.
Written by Ben Haggerty, Ryan Lewis, Tricia Davis.
The truck slows down.
Directed by Ryan Lewis, Jason Koenig, Jon Jon Augustavo.
Produced by Tricia Davis, Honna Kimmerer, Jenny Koenig.
Macklemore sits on the couch, looking at his phone. The truck pulls over to a stop.
Logo. Red Digital Cinema. Shot on Red.
